'''Annihilator 1''' was the designation of [[Colonel/Legends|Colonel]] [[Beri Tulon]]'s personal [[All Terrain Armored Transport/Legends|All Terrain Armored Transport]]. Annihilator 1 was used in the [[Massacre on Abridon]] as part of [[Tulon's task force]]. Tulon, in an attempt to defect to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]], turned it against the rest of his force and headed Annihilator 1 towards the Rebel base, but the walker was brought down by the forces of [[General/Legends|General]] [[Brenn Tantor]], Tulon's old student. Tantor was shocked to discover that Tulon, pulled out of the wreckage, was the defector and not a subordinate but nevertheless did his duty and had Tulon taken into custody and sent to [[Tarkin Detention Facility]] on [[Ruul (planet)|Ruul]].

